<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Smart Exchange</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .about-us {
            padding: 80px 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            text-align: center;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in;
        }

        .intro {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
            color: #555;
            animation: slideUp 1s ease-out;
        }

        .content {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px; /* Reduced gap for tighter layout */
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .content-box {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #e8f0fe 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; /* Added for hover */
        }

        .content-box:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03); /* Slight scale up on hover */
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); /* Enhanced shadow on hover */
        }

        .content-box h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .content-box h2::after {
            content: '';
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #34c759;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 0;
        }

        .content-box p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 0; /* No bottom margin since it’s the only paragraph */
        }

        .team {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }

        .team h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 20px 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .team-member {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 25px 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .team-member:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .team-member img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 3px solid #34c759;
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 0; /* Remove padding from content, handled by content-box */
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
            }
            .intro {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }
            .content-box {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .content-box h2 {
                font-size: 1.6em;
            }
            .team {
                padding: 0 10px;
            }
            .team-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
                padding: 15px 0;
            }
            .team-member {
                padding: 20px 10px;
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            .team-member img {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
            .team-member h3 {
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }
            .team-member p {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .content-box {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            .team-member {
                padding: 15px 8px;
            }
            .team-member img {
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
            }
            .team-member h3 {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }
            .team-member p {
                font-size: 0.85em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %> 
    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Smart Exchange</h1>
            <p class="intro">
                At Smart Exchange, we believe in giving tech a second life. We’re passionate about refurbishing devices to deliver high-quality, affordable solutions while reducing e-waste.
            </p>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h2>Our Journey</h2>
                    <p>
                        Launched in 2021, Smart Exchange began with a vision to make premium technology accessible to everyone. We’ve since refurbished thousands of devices, blending innovation with sustainability.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>
                        We’re here to provide top-tier refurbished smartphones, laptops, and gadgets that rival new ones in performance—all while championing a greener planet. Trust, quality, and eco-friendliness drive everything we do.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-box">
                    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                    <p>
                        We aim to lead the refurbished tech industry by setting new standards in quality and sustainability, ensuring every device we touch contributes to a circular economy and a brighter future.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="team">
                <h2>Our Team</h2>
                <div class="team-grid">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Team Member 1" onerror="this.src='data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAACklEQVR4nGMAAQAABQABDQottAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='">
                        <h3>Member1</h3>
                        <p>Founder</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Team Member 2" onerror="this.src='data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAACklEQVR4nGMAAQAABQABDQottAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='">
                        <h3>Member2</h3>
                        <p> co Founder</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Team Member 3" onerror="this.src='data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAACklEQVR4nGMAAQAABQABDQottAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='">
                        <h3>Member3</h3>
                        <p>Customer Experience</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
